{"tid":1693093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無用㗎你哋，走啦和理非】呢句可能係黑警講嘅唯一真話","createTime":"2019-11-04T11:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:02:23.000Z","uid":59815,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"834b30b34f4e3f49eae4e2465baf342d1469efed","tid":1693093,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"致和理非：<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知星期日啲黑警喺鑽石山荷里活廣場點鬧你哋，佢話「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無用㗎你哋，走啦和理非</span></span>」，老老豆豆，呢句可能係黑警唔係無道理，如果你唔想做無用嘅和理非，你唔係淨係要做啲行動仔咁簡單，係要叫埋其他人做呀﹗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非唔撚係淺黃呀﹗淺黃就話遊吓行、打吓卡啫﹗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非，你嘅責任係要多走一步呀﹗(唔係叫你去死呀﹗)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聽日(11月5日)係全民口罩日，後日(11月6日)都有工會發起車長口罩日</strong></span>，你哋啲和理非，唔好以為帶住口罩就做咗嘢，你起碼要叫十個人拎口罩，仲要帶多盒口罩放喺巴士上面俾人攞，你先好叫自己做和理非，如果唔係，你只係淺黃咋﹗明未呀﹗<br />\n<br />\n濕鳩和理非，你哋係運動俾人笑鳩好耐喇﹗生性啲啦﹗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAe2tUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAe2tUd.jpg&h=08584781&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BeBykU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BeBykU.jpg&h=b10d89f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8iFZ0U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8iFZ0U.jpg&h=bed41702&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMrDMFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMrDMFV.jpg&h=3f365a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gejt8Ug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgejt8Ug.jpg&h=ba233233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d173db5b66a4c970144da3dcdfa56e1099345","tid":1693093,"uid":182185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" data-